# jsw-nx
> Next toolkit for python.

## installation
```shell
pip install jsw-nx -U
```

## usage
```python
import jsw_nx as nx

## common methods
nx.includes([1,2,3], 2) # => True
nx.includes([1,2,3], 5) # => False
```
